    <h1>Backlinks</h1>
    <p class="description">Links from other websites that point to yours. Google treats them as <strong>votes of confidence</strong> and uses their quality, relevance, and anchor text as core inputs to search rankings.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
